text: Liberty Chakoroma (born 28 February 1994) is a Zimbabwean footballer who plays as a defender for Chicken Inn F.C. and the Zimbabwe national football team. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1994 births Category:Living people Category:Zimbabwean footballers Category:Zimbabwe international footballers Category:Sportspeople from Mutare Category:Association football defenders Category:Buffaloes F.C. players Category:Free State Stars F.C. players Category:Ngezi Platinum F.C. players Category:Chicken Inn F.C. players Category:Zimbabwe Premier Soccer League players Category:South African Premier Division players Category:Zimbabwean expatriate footballers Category:Expatriate soccer players in South Africa Category:Zimbabwean expatriate sportspeople in South Africa
